products.title: Antique White PerfectFIT Venetian Blind
products.metadescription: Off white with a hint of cream, this matt perfectfit antique white venetian blind brings a little warmth along with brightness.If white will just be too bright and cool then the antique white slat colour may well be perfect in more ways than one.
